text: Homonoea flavescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1958. It is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Homonoea flavescens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1958
title: Homonoea flavescens
